        Retrieve a parameter in the metadata.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of the value to get.

      • getParameter

        <T> T getParameter(Object key,
                 T def)
        Retrieve a parameter in the metadata.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of the value to get.
        Parameters:
        key - the parameter's key.
        def - a default value to return if no parameter with the specified key can be found.
        Returns:
        the parameter's value or null if no parameter with the specified key exists.

      • setParameter

        void setParameter(Object key,
                Object value)
        Set a parameter in the metadata. If a parameter with the same key already exists, its value is replaced with the new one.
        Parameters:
        key - the parameter's key.
        value - the parameter's value.

      • removeParameter

        <T> T removeParameter(Object key)
        Remove a parameter from the metadata.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of the value to remove.
        Parameters:
        key - the parameter's key.
        Returns:
        the removed parameter's value or null if no parameter with the specified key exists.
